name: Iconly 3D 🚀 770+ Essential icons
description:
Iconly 3D is designed and rendered in 4K quality with the utmost care.


1. Family style

The main feature of this style is the same color palette, material, and exposure that has been observed in more than 190 icons.


2. Clay style

In this style, white Clay material is used, which is suitable for most design environments


3. Dark style

Due to the importance of dark theme in recent phones and devices, this style solves the need for this section with a black color palette.


4. Real Style

This is our favorite style and you can see the most carefully designed details by zooming in.
